      <h3>Stacks</h3>
      <p>A template library that allows a snapshot to be taken of an underlying server configuration
        for any project. The snapshot can then be applied to new projects or replace the stack on an
        existing one.</p>
      <h3>Starter Packs</h3>
      <p>A combination of a Stack (see above) and code. Most often used as a way of providing
